      <h3>
       Cascadia Resilience Short Course
      </h3>
      This course will provide engineering practitioners and related professionals with an in-depth understanding of hazards posed by the Cascadia Subduction Zone and identify effective solution technologies to build more resilient communities.
     </p>
     July 14, 2016, 8:30 a.m. – 6:30 p.m.
     <br>
      Kearney Hall, Oregon State University
      <br>
